    <!--
         ==========================================================================
          S6.10  DUR TABELALARI
          'STOP' on the climb and 'DUR' on the descent, standing on the LEFT of travel beside the painted line the vehicle has to hold on for 2 s. Round plates like the tabelalar but inverted - white on red - so a stop instruction can never be read as a stage number.
         ==========================================================================
    -->
